  "body_html": "<!doctype html><div data-lake-element=\"root\" class=\"lake-engine lake-typography-traditional\" data-parser-by=\"lake2html\"><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/kubernetes/dashboard\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Kubernetes Dashboard</a> 是基于网页的 Kubernetes 用户界面。</p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\"><span data-card-type=\"inline\" data-lake-card=\"image\" data-card-value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fd33wubrfki0l68.cloudfront.net%2F349824f68836152722dab89465835e604719caea%2F6e0b7%2Fimages%2Fdocs%2Fui-dashboard.png%22%2C%22alt%22%3A%22%22%7D\"><img data-role=\"image\" src=\"https://d33wubrfki0l68.cloudfront.net/349824f68836152722dab89465835e604719caea/6e0b7/images/docs/ui-dashboard.png\" data-raw-src=\"https://d33wubrfki0l68.cloudfront.net/349824f68836152722dab89465835e604719caea/6e0b7/images/docs/ui-dashboard.png\" class=\"image lake-drag-image\" style=\"border: none; box-shadow: none; visibility: visible;\"></span></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><a name=\"部署\"></a><h2 id=\"a9f94dcd\" style=\"padding: 7px 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 24px; line-height: 32px;\">部署</h2><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\">执行以下命令即可部署 Dashboard：</p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><div data-card-type=\"block\" data-lake-card=\"codeblock\" data-card-value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22b196bdc8%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22bash%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22kubectl%20apply%20-f%20https%3A%2F%2Fraw.githubusercontent.com%2Fkubernetes%2Fdashboard%2Fv2.0.0-beta8%2Faio%2Fdeploy%2Frecommended.yaml%22%7D\" id=\"b196bdc8\"><div class=\"lake-codeblock-content\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(232, 232, 232); max-width: 750px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><div class=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 16px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><pre class=\"cm-s-default\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><span class=\"lake-preview-line\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><span class=\"lake-preview-line-number lake-lm-pad-level-0\" style=\"color: rgb(191, 191, 191); margin: 0px 8px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"></span><span class=\"lake-preview-codeblock-content\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">kubectl apply -f https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kubernetes/dashboard/v2.0.0-beta8/aio/deploy/recommended.yaml</span></span></pre></div></div></div><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><a name=\"访问\"></a><h2 id=\"d5c0ebde\" style=\"padding: 7px 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 24px; line-height: 32px;\">访问</h2><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\">通过命令行代理访问，执行以下命令：</p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><div data-card-type=\"block\" data-lake-card=\"codeblock\" data-card-value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22c62db0fd%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22bash%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%24%20kubectl%20proxy%22%7D\" id=\"c62db0fd\"><div class=\"lake-codeblock-content\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(232, 232, 232); max-width: 750px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><div class=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 16px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><pre class=\"cm-s-default\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><span class=\"lake-preview-line\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><span class=\"lake-preview-line-number lake-lm-pad-level-0\" style=\"color: rgb(191, 191, 191); margin: 0px 8px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"></span><span class=\"lake-preview-codeblock-content\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">$ kubectl proxy</span></span></pre></div></div></div><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\">到 <a href=\"http://localhost:8001/api/v1/namespaces/kubernetes-dashboard/services/https:kubernetes-dashboard:/proxy/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">http://localhost:8001/api/v1/namespaces/kubernetes-dashboard/services/https:kubernetes-dashboard:/proxy/</a> 即可访问。</p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><a name=\"登录\"></a><h2 id=\"402d19e5\" style=\"padding: 7px 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 24px; line-height: 32px;\">登录</h2><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\">目前，Dashboard 仅支持使用 Bearer 令牌登录。下面教大家如何创建该令牌：</p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><div data-card-type=\"block\" data-lake-card=\"codeblock\" data-card-value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%222cacbbcf%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22bash%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%24%20kubectl%20create%20sa%20dashboard-admin%20-n%20kube-system%5Cn%5Cn%24%20kubectl%20create%20clusterrolebinding%20dashboard-admin%20--clusterrole%3Dcluster-admin%20--serviceaccount%3Dkube-system%3Adashboard-admin%5Cn%5Cn%24%20ADMIN_SECRET%3D%24(kubectl%20get%20secrets%20-n%20kube-system%20%7C%20grep%20dashboard-admin%20%7C%20awk%20'%7Bprint%20%241%7D')%5Cn%5Cn%24%20DASHBOARD_LOGIN_TOKEN%3D%24(kubectl%20describe%20secret%20-n%20kube-system%20%24%7BADMIN_SECRET%7D%20%7C%20grep%20-E%20'%5Etoken'%20%7C%20awk%20'%7Bprint%20%242%7D')%5Cn%5Cnecho%20%24%7BDASHBOARD_LOGIN_TOKEN%7D%22%7D\" id=\"2cacbbcf\"><div class=\"lake-codeblock-content\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(232, 232, 232); max-width: 750px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: rgb(249, 249, 249);\"><div class=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 16px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><pre class=\"cm-s-default\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><span class=\"lake-preview-line\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><span class=\"lake-preview-line-number lake-lm-pad-level-0\" style=\"color: rgb(191, 191, 191); margin: 0px 8px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"></span><span class=\"lake-preview-codeblock-content\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">$ kubectl create sa dashboard-admin -n kube-system\n</span></span><span class=\"lake-preview-line\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><span class=\"lake-preview-line-number lake-lm-pad-level-0\" style=\"color: rgb(191, 191, 191); margin: 0px 8px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"></span><span class=\"lake-preview-codeblock-content\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">\n</span></span><span class=\"lake-preview-line\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><span class=\"lake-preview-line-number lake-lm-pad-level-0\" style=\"color: rgb(191, 191, 191); margin: 0px 8px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"></span><span class=\"lake-preview-codeblock-content\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">$ kubectl create clusterrolebinding dashboard-admin --clusterrole=cluster-admin --serviceaccount=kube-system:dashboard-admin\n</span></span><span class=\"lake-preview-line\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><span class=\"lake-preview-line-number lake-lm-pad-level-0\" style=\"color: rgb(191, 191, 191); margin: 0px 8px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"></span><span class=\"lake-preview-codeblock-content\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">\n</span></span><span class=\"lake-preview-line\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><span class=\"lake-preview-line-number lake-lm-pad-level-0\" style=\"color: rgb(191, 191, 191); margin: 0px 8px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"></span><span class=\"lake-preview-codeblock-content\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">$ ADMIN_SECRET=$(kubectl get secrets -n kube-system | grep dashboard-admin | awk '{print $1}')\n</span></span><span class=\"lake-preview-line\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><span class=\"lake-preview-line-number lake-lm-pad-level-0\" style=\"color: rgb(191, 191, 191); margin: 0px 8px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"></span><span class=\"lake-preview-codeblock-content\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">\n</span></span><span class=\"lake-preview-line\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><span class=\"lake-preview-line-number lake-lm-pad-level-0\" style=\"color: rgb(191, 191, 191); margin: 0px 8px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"></span><span class=\"lake-preview-codeblock-content\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">$ DASHBOARD_LOGIN_TOKEN=$(kubectl describe secret -n kube-system ${ADMIN_SECRET} | grep -E '^token' | awk '{print $2}')\n</span></span><span class=\"lake-preview-line\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><span class=\"lake-preview-line-number lake-lm-pad-level-0\" style=\"color: rgb(191, 191, 191); margin: 0px 8px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"></span><span class=\"lake-preview-codeblock-content\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">\n</span></span><span class=\"lake-preview-line\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><span class=\"lake-preview-line-number lake-lm-pad-level-0\" style=\"color: rgb(191, 191, 191); margin: 0px 8px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"></span><span class=\"lake-preview-codeblock-content\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">echo ${DASHBOARD_LOGIN_TOKEN}</span></span></pre></div></div></div><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\">将结果粘贴到登录页面，即可登录。</p><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><a name=\"参考文档\"></a><h2 id=\"d1f972b3\" style=\"padding: 7px 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 24px; line-height: 32px;\">参考文档</h2><p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.74; margin: 0px;\"><br></p><ul lake-indent=\"0\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; margin: 0px; padding-left: 23px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); line-height: 1.74; letter-spacing: 0.05em; outline-style: none; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><li><a href=\"https://kubernetes.io/zh/docs/tasks/access-application-cluster/web-ui-dashboard/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">官方文档</a></li></ul></div>",
